# Flycast Project Structure

Follow the structure from the technical spec:

```
flycast/
├── app/
│   ├── layout.tsx              # Root layout
│   ├── page.tsx                # Public board (/)
│   ├── admin/
│   │   ├── page.tsx            # Admin dashboard (/admin)
│   │   └── qr/
│   │       └── page.tsx        # QR code display (/admin/qr)
│   └── globals.css             # Tailwind global styles
├── components/
│   ├── MessageCard.tsx         # Single message display
│   ├── MessageFeed.tsx         # Real-time message list
│   ├── ComposeMessage.tsx      # Text input + dictate + send
│   ├── MessageHistory.tsx     # Admin message history with edit
│   ├── PasswordGate.tsx        # Simple password prompt
│   ├── QRCodeDisplay.tsx      # QR code generator
│   └── SpeechToText.tsx        # Web Speech API component
├── hooks/
│   └── useRealtimeMessages.ts  # Shared Supabase subscription + connection state
├── lib/
│   ├── supabase.ts            # Supabase client initialization
│   └── types.ts               # TypeScript types
├── actions/
│   └── auth.ts                # Server Action: verify admin password
```

Use these exact component names. Place new logic in the appropriate folder.
